race.comment: BEAUER (3) is yet to break through this campaign but is knocking on the door, chasing gamely again into the placings last start at Moruya. Peak fitness now, expect her to take some stopping. STAR LEGACY (1) has been leaving himself with too much to do but closing off well. Expecting Keatings to have him closer this time and poised to strike. OBVIOUSLY ALBERT (8) likes to leave it late. Was good last time at Goulburn when getting with a length of the winner. Watch for him charging if they overdo it early. SIR SUBLIME (4) has been better recently and is a two-time winner over this journey. Worth keeping safe.
